commentable_entity.title: Stop Amber Heard Gaslighting US
commentable_entity.description: Request that the Main stream media stop giving airtime to Amber Heard and her representatives with them claiming to represent those of US who ARE victims- it is disgusting. She DOES NOT represent US. You must stop allowing her a platform to spew these lies. We also demand the ACLU immediately REMOVE Amber Heard as an ambassador and L’Oréal cancel her contract. She has admitted to hitting Mr Depp, she has been arrested for hitting her ex girlfriend. She is not exactly a representative to speak against domestic violence, regardless of whether she is or isn’t a victim she has displayed that she is a perpetrator. She is now a PROVEN LIAR. Given the current condition her presence on the Website is an affront to those who have truly been victimized and we will boycott you as long as you are supporting the abuser gaslighting us.
